front.title: •Admiral Motti (V)
front.gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots.  Chiraneau may not modify your Force drains.  Kuat Drive Yards is [Immune to Alter].  Unless your Senate on table, unique (•) Star Destroyers are power +2 and immunity to attrition +1.  Once per game, may deploy non-[Set 0] Kuat Drive Yards from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Senior Navy Commander of Death Star. Believes in technology. Ridiculed the Force. Ambitious leader. Promoted due to support of New Order, not military skills. Hates Vader.

combo: Admiral Motti (V) + Lone Pilot Add two battle destiny if Motti is defending a battle alone at a system.
Admiral Motti (V) + Vader's Eye + Lone Warrior Add two battle destiny if Motti is defending a battle alone at a site.
